  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist Shop Crush on Steam</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321030/extras/6e7262205fbc2e530d5c9c12dc8ab388.avif?t=1759957052\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hey friends!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you survived</strong> <strong>ONE DAY for Ched</strong> <i>(or at least laughed at it)</i>, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Why not wishlist our new game</strong> — <i>Shop Crush?</i>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It’s very different:</strong> <i>narrative, weird, full of illusions.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your wishlist helps us finish it</strong>, <i>and you’ll probably get a game you actually enjoy :)</i></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321030/extras/29ae9b850aadb75503377d66a3ac416e.poster.avif?t=1759957052\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321030/extras/29ae9b850aadb75503377d66a3ac416e.webm?t=1759957052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321030/extras/29ae9b850aadb75503377d66a3ac416e.mp4?t=1759957052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DIVE INTO THE WORLD OF OLD SCHOOL <i>Ched </i> SHOOTERS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight the monsters, shoot 'em up with your skills and powerful guns. Complete the whole story and find out the secrets of Ched's mind. ONE DAY for Ched makes you feel like you're back in the glory days of gaming, and brings you the ultimate in hardcore gameplay, interesting story, and quest elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your gaming skills to complete the levels and kill all enemies. Victory can be yours, but you will have to fight hard. ONE DAY, Ched will never forgive your mistakes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321030/extras/0bbd0c5b4ccca4ad9a41060d854704f8.poster.avif?t=1759957052\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321030/extras/0bbd0c5b4ccca4ad9a41060d854704f8.webm?t=1759957052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321030/extras/0bbd0c5b4ccca4ad9a41060d854704f8.mp4?t=1759957052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ULTIMATE HARDCORE GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player skills mean everything in the world of ONE DAY for Ched. No saves, no health recovering, no margin for error! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COMIC / CARTOON ART STYLE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-game graphics are cell-shaded with cartoon-ish render. The story features hand-drawn comics that reveal Ched's story.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EASY TO ENGAGE, HARDCORE TO STAY ENGAGED</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ONE DAY for Ched runs on a weak PC, has its own charming humor, catchy phrases, low price, and trade cards.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321030/extras/29ae9b850aadb75503377d66a3ac416e.poster.avif?t=1759957052\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321030/extras/29ae9b850aadb75503377d66a3ac416e.webm?t=1759957052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321030/extras/29ae9b850aadb75503377d66a3ac416e.mp4?t=1759957052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DIVE INTO THE WORLD OF OLD SCHOOL <i>Ched </i> SHOOTERS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight the monsters, shoot 'em up with your skills and powerful guns. Complete the whole story and find out the secrets of Ched's mind. ONE DAY for Ched makes you feel like you're back in the glory days of gaming, and brings you the ultimate in hardcore gameplay, interesting story, and quest elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your gaming skills to complete the levels and kill all enemies. Victory can be yours, but you will have to fight hard. ONE DAY, Ched will never forgive your mistakes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321030/extras/0bbd0c5b4ccca4ad9a41060d854704f8.poster.avif?t=1759957052\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321030/extras/0bbd0c5b4ccca4ad9a41060d854704f8.webm?t=1759957052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/321030/extras/0bbd0c5b4ccca4ad9a41060d854704f8.mp4?t=1759957052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ULTIMATE HARDCORE GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player skills mean everything in the world of ONE DAY for Ched. No saves, no health recovering, no margin for error! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COMIC / CARTOON ART STYLE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-game graphics are cell-shaded with cartoon-ish render. The story features hand-drawn comics that reveal Ched's story.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EASY TO ENGAGE, HARDCORE TO STAY ENGAGED</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ONE DAY for Ched runs on a weak PC, has its own charming humor, catchy phrases, low price, and trade cards.</p>",
